FORMANCE \n\nDEFINITION \n\n\u2022 \n\nIf the patient\u2019s functional status varies during the look back period, record their \nusual ability to perform each activity.  \n\n\u2022  For GG0130 and GG0170, a patient\u2019s usual performance is their ability greater \n\nthan 50% of the time during the look back period. \n\n\u2022  Follow-up Performance: Clinicians should code the patient\u2019s functional status based on a functional", "type": "Document"}}